---
import { FOOTER_LINKS, SITE } from '../data/site';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="mt-20 border-t border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/60">
  <div class="container-page py-14">
    <div class="grid gap-10 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5">
      <div class="lg:pr-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <img src="/logo.svg" alt="Telegram" width="36" height="36" class="h-9 w-9" />
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Telegram</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500">
          Telegram（纸飞机 / 飞机）中文下载导航站，汇总各平台官方安全下载入口与简体中文设置教程。
        </p>
      </div>

      {FOOTER_LINKS.map((col) => (
        <nav aria-label={col.title}>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">{col.title}</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2.5">
            {col.links.map((l) => (
              <li>
                <a href={l.href} class="text-sm text-slate-500 no-underline hover:text-tg-600">{l.label}</a>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </nav>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-4 gap-y-1.5 text-xs text-slate-500">
      <span class="font-semibold text-slate-700">友情链接</span>
      <a href="https://sites.google.com/view/atgpc/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-slate-500 no-underline hover:text-tg-600">sites.google.com/view/atgpc</a>
      <a href="https://sites.google.com/view/telegramsa/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-slate-500 no-underline hover:text-tg-600">sites.google.com/view/telegramsa</a>
      <a href="https://wschats.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-slate-500 no-underline hover:text-tg-600">旺商聊官网</a>
      <a href="https://qshuiyy.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-slate-500 no-underline hover:text-tg-600">汽水音乐</a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 border-t border-slate-200 pt-6 text-xs text-slate-500 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
      <p>© {year} {SITE.domain} · 本站为第三方下载导航，所有下载均指向 Telegram 官方源（telegram.org）。Telegram® 为 Telegram FZ-LLC 商标。</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <a href="/sitemap-index.xml" class="text-slate-500 no-underline hover:text-tg-600">站点地图</a>
        <a href="/rss.xml" class="text-slate-500 no-underline hover:text-tg-600">RSS</a>
        <a href="/faq/" class="text-slate-500 no-underline hover:text-tg-600">FAQ</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
